    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>caramelised pepper & onion </strong>to a bowl and reserve the pan</p><p>Add<strong> half</strong> of your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!) to the bowl with 1/2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir through the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> – this is your<strong> pepper & onion salsa</strong></p>",
