    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated chicken skewers</strong> and cook for 4 min, turning so they brown on all sides</p><p>Once browned, reduce the heat to medium-high, cover with a lid and cook for a further 6 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>smoky chicken skewers</strong></p>",
