    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with the <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>spicy mayo</strong></p>",
